Password command

# dnpasswd -i username -> will give the details of the user password info

If password is locked, use the below command. 

# dnpasswd -u username

Reset password, use the below command.

# dnpasswd -r username  --> to reset the password and it will display the password on tty

send it to the user's personal email

# passwd-email -u <username> -m -p    -p = personal mail id

Users can change the password using the below mentioned link ater 24 hours.

http://intranet.zro.dneg.com/password/change

